  "title": "Assistant Contracts Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and analyze cost comparison</li>\n  <li>Obtaining quotations, liaising and negotiate with sub-contractors and suppliers</li>\n  <li>Responsible for measuring quantities and taking off</li>\n  <li>Prepare Variation Orders, claims, final accounts, settlement and sub-contractor payments</li>\n  <li>All other contracts management related job</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree / Diploma in Building or its equivalent</li>\n  <li>Min 8 years and above experience as deputy contracts in main-con companies</li>\n  <li>Proven ability in contract negotiation, contract administration &amp; variation orders</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently, be meticulous, analytical with excellent problem-solving skills, proactive, a good team player &amp; able to meet tight deadlines</li>\n</ul>",
